---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy | Jotter">
  <div class="privacy-body">
    <div class="container">

      <header>
        <span class="brand">OPEN APPS LABS</span>
        <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
        <div class="meta-info">
          <span>App: Jotter</span>
          <span>Effective: January 8, 2026</span>
        </div>
      </header>

      <div class="summary-box">
        <p style="margin-bottom: 0;">
          <strong>Short Version:</strong> Your notes are yours. Jotter is an offline-first app. 
          I do not have access to your notes, passwords, or any content you create within the app.
        </p>
      </div>

      <section>
        <h2>01. Data Storage</h2>
        <p>
          <strong>Jotter</strong> operates on an "Offline First" principle.
        </p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Local Database:</strong> All notes and folders are stored in a local SQLite (Room) database on your device.</li>
            <li><strong>No Cloud Sync:</strong> This app does not sync data to any cloud server or third-party service. If you uninstall the app without backing up, your data is removed by the Android OS.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>02. Permissions</h2>
        <p>The app requests minimal permissions to function:</p>

        <ul>
          <li><strong>BIOMETRIC_ID</strong><br>
            <span class="sub-text">Used solely to unlock secured notes or the app itself if you enable the security feature. Biometric data is handled by the Android System and is never accessed by the app directly.</span>
          </li>
          <li><strong>READ/WRITE STORAGE</strong> (Optional)<br>
            <span class="sub-text">Required only if you use the Backup & Restore feature to save a copy of your notes to your device's file system.</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>03. Analytics</h2>
        <p>
          I do not use Google Analytics, Firebase, or any other tracking software. I do not know how many notes you have or what you write.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>04. Contact</h2>
        <p class="contact-area">
          <a href="mailto:openappslabs@gmail.com">openappslabs@gmail.com</a>
        </p>
      </section>

      <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2026 Open Apps Labs. All rights reserved.</p>
      </footer>

    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
    /* Reuse the variables and styles from the 5G Privacy page */
    :root { --bg-color: #000000; --card-bg: #121212; --text-primary: #ffffff; --text-secondary: #aaaaaa; --accent-red: #d71921; --border-color: #333333; --font-mono: 'Roboto Mono', monospace; --font-sans: 'Inter', sans-serif; }
    .privacy-body { background-color: var(--bg-color); color: var(--text-primary); font-family: var(--font-sans); line-height: 1.6; padding: 40px 20px; display: flex; justify-content: center; min-height: 100vh; }
    .container { max-width: 800px; width: 100%; }
    header { margin-bottom: 60px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color); padding-bottom: 40px; }
    .brand { font-family: var(--font-mono); font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: -1px; margin-bottom: 20px; display: block; color: var(--text-primary); }
    h1 { font-family: var(--font-sans); font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3rem); font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: -0.02em; margin-bottom: 16px; color: var(--text-primary); }
    .meta-info { display: flex; gap: 20px; font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--text-secondary); }
    section { margin-bottom: 40px; }
    h2 { font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 1.1rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px; color: var(--text-secondary); margin-bottom: 16px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; }
    h2::after { content: ''; height: 1px; background: var(--border-color); flex-grow: 1; }
    p { margin-bottom: 16px; font-weight: 300; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9); }
    ul { list-style: none; margin-bottom: 16px; background: var(--card-bg); border-radius: 12px; padding: 20px; border: 1px solid var(--border-color); }
    li { margin-bottom: 10px; padding-left: 20px; position: relative; }
    li::before { content: '>'; position: absolute; left: 0; color: var(--accent-red); font-family: var(--font-mono); font-weight: 700; }
    strong { font-weight: 600; color: var(--text-primary); }
    .sub-text { font-size: 0.9rem; color: #888; }
    .summary-box { background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05); border-left: 4px solid var(--accent-red); padding: 20px; border-radius: 0 12px 12px 0; margin-bottom: 40px; }
    footer { margin-top: 80px; padding-top: 40px; border-top: 1px solid var(--border-color); font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--text-secondary); text-align: center; }
    a { color: var(--text-primary); text-decoration: underline; text-decoration-color: var(--accent-red); }
    a:hover { color: var(--accent-red); }
    .contact-area { font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 1.1rem; margin-top: 20px; }
</style>